data.title: Famous People Who Died in June 1949
data.meta_description: Famous deaths in June 1949. Learn about 10 historical figures, notable people and celebrities who died in Jun 1949 like Amadeo Giannini.
data.text:
Dynam-Victor Fumet, French composer, dies at 82

Amadeo Giannini

American banker and entrepreneur (founded Bank of America), dies at 79

John T. McCutcheon, American cartoonist (Pulitzer Prize-1931), dies at 79

Jun 10 Sigrid Undset, Danish-born Norwegian writer (Kristin Lavransdatter, 1928 Nobel Prize for Literature), dies at 67

Koci Xoxe, Albanian vice-premier, executed

Jun 11 Oton Zupanic, Slavs poet (Zimzelen pod snegom), dies at 71

Syed Zafarul Hasan, Indian-Pakistani Prominent Muslim philosopher, dies at 64

Buck Freeman, American baseball outfielder (World Series 1903; HR leader 1899, 1903; AL RBI leader 1902, 03; Boston Americans), dies at 77

Kim Gu, President of the Provisional Government of the Republic of Korea (1939-48), dies at 72

Walter Giffen, Australian cricketer "one of the worst Test batsmen of all time" (brother of George, 3 Tests), dies at 87
